# User preferences

The bot reads this on startup and writes it after every change. The
SQLite table `user_preferences` is the source of truth — manual edits
here are reloaded on the next bot restart.

Add long-lived instructions through chat ("請以後跟我說繁體中文",
"always cite sources before claims") and they'll show up here. Avoid
storing secrets / passwords / API keys — the bot's sensitivity filter
will reject them anyway.

## Communication

- language: 繁體中文 (example — added 2026-05-09 via ws)
- tone: 簡潔 (example)

## Workflow

- never auto-execute irreversible actions, always ask first (example)
- prefer Porkbun over Cloudflare for domain pricing (example)

## Notification

- only push major findings, debounce 30 min (example)
